sub_title: Streamlining operational processes through automation. Making a difference is my passion and I love doing it at bunq ðŸš€
summary:
Currently an impact-driven senior process engineer, formerly a professional dancer, creative director, sales agent, team leader, financial crime specialist and more.

Since I joined bunq I have had endless growth opportunities and as you will see below in my profile, I have turned my career around multiple times. After specialising in a more regulatory role I began my journey as a team leader. Though I enjoyed my position immensely, working in a fin-tech company had already sparkled my curiosity about the tech side of things. ðŸ¤“

This is why I stepped down as a leader in January 2023 and restarted my career. I had to learn from scratch about process automation and frontend development. I have recently taken a step further by diving into AI. Who knows what comes next!

And even though my work has changed a lot throughout the years, my hobbies have remained the same. In my free time you can find me dancing, jogging in the park, learning a new language or travelling around. ðŸ•º

Process Automation I Internal Process Tooling I Project Management |  Leadership
